  • Constructor Details

    • Movie

      public Movie(String title, MovieStatusType status, String synopsis, String director, ArrayList<String> cast, MovieType type, LocalDateTime endOfShowingDate)
      Creates a new Movie listing, with information keyed in by the Admin.
      Parameters:
      title - Title of the new Movie.
      status - Status of the new Movie (ie. COMING_SOON, PREVIEW, NOW_SHOWING, END_OF_SHOWING).
      synopsis - Synopsis of what this new Movie is about.
      director - Name of the director of the new Movie.
      cast - List of the names of the cast members.
      type - Type of the new Movie (ie. REGULAR, 3D, BLOCKBUSTER).
      endOfShowingDate - Date invalid input: '&' Time when the new Movie stops airing.

    • compareTo

      public int compareTo(Movie m)
      Helper method to sort 2 different Movies in alphabetical order. Case-Insensitive.
      Specified by:
      compareTo in interface Comparable<Movie>
      Parameters:
      m - Another Movie to compare this Movie with.
      Returns:
      -1 when this Movie's Title is lexicographically less than the provided Movie's Title (ignoring case). 0 when both Movie's Titles are equal (ignoring case). 1 when this Movie's Title is lexicographically greater than the provided Movie's Title (ignoring case).
